ient Slider\n  * [x] Color Plane (2-axis picker)\n  * [x] Color Swatch with Alpha Grid\n  * [ ] Swatch Grid\n  * [ ] Tab Deck\n  * [ ] Tree View\n* [ ] Implement opinionated editor layout components (post-BSN)\n  * [ ] Page layout variants\n  * [ ] Toolbar\n  * [ ] Sidebar\n\nSpin-off tasks:\n* [x] Rounding options for sliders and other numeric inputs\n* [ ] UI Transition animations framework: switch slider, disclosure triangle rotate, dialog enter/exit\n* [x] #20499\n* [ ] Verify that variable-width fonts work in Bevy, and then replace FiraSans.\n* [ ] Focus Rings\n* [ ] #20524\n* [x] Add Reflection support to CoreWidgets\n\n@alice-i-cecile ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/19236/reactions","total_count":27,"+1":19,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":8,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/19236/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"actor":{"login":"amedoeyes","id":37800919,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM3ODAwOTE5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/37800919?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes","html_url":"https://github.com/amedoeyes","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/amedoeyes/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2025-08-13T03:45:09Z","upda